Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Oujia Board's Death Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So by destroying Dark Necrofear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Field Magic Dark Sanctuary is activated...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what could Bakura be planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment Dark Sanctuary is activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Hateful Spirit, known as the Onryou, is automatically Special Summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That vengeful soul, knowing only hatred, will wander your field in search of its next host...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't see which Monster is possesses until it's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have no clue what it is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Currently, Bakura has no Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I directly attack Bakura with Magnet Warrior Gamma,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've just got to give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I direct attack with Magnet Warrior Gamma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Burn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out of Magnet Warrior Gamma and attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be really shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been possessed by the Hateful Spirit of Dark Sanctuary, the Onryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Onryou becomes an Equipment Card
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attached itself to one of the opponent's Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's inside of my Magnet Warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Onryou is more than happy to attack when you order it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,although {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who takes the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the player who is attacked loses half of the possessed Monster's Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's half of Magnet Warrior Gamma's 1500 Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,totaling at 750 points that will be drained from your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the 750 points {\i1}you{\i0} lost will be added to {\i1}my{\i0} Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You absorbed my Life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to get {\i1}surprised{\i0}, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is but the {\i1}start{\i0} of my Occult Deck's terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then play my Permanent Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouija Board, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that weird looking board?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tool they use in Western spiritualism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Spiritualism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's similar to a planchette, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really... creeps me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouija Board...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ouija board is a tool to communicate with spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planchette will point to letters on the board, and spell out the spirit's wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, the spirits will send you a letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The letter "D" appeared on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be much more than just "D"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next turn, the letters "E", "A", "T" and "H"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will appear one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-E-A-T-H"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Death"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when all the letters of "death" mark the message of demise,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even {\i1}if{\i0} you still have Life remaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be eliminated right on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means I only have four turns left...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he let me beat Dark Necrofear on purpose so he could play this combo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Yugi only has four turns left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using the Onryou to possess Yugi's Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...stealing his Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and using the Ouija Board to put a time limit on this match with a message of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess he {\b0}did{\b1} have a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The countdown to your doom has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have four turns left to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's {\i1}much{\i0} more to the Occult Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! The Dark Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can only attack with one Monster each turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm about to play another terrifying card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then Summon Earthbound Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to sacrifice this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Permanent Field Magic Dark Sanctuary requires a sacrifice each and every turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of the Effect of the The Dark Door Magic Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only attack with one Monster per turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magnet Warrior Gamma is possessed by the Onryou, so it can't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura doesn't have a wall Monster on his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I attack him directly with the Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...since Bakura only has 900 Life Points, he'll be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's a good chance he's realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if he has... there's no doubt in my mind his Reverse Card is a Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}wrong{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't waste this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it {\b0}is{\b1} a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I've got to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll place Kuriboh on the field in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I attack with Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Burn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he got the {\i1}Black Magician Girl{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And half of the Black Magician Girl's 2500 Attack Points
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will come out of your Life, Yugi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and be added to my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hateful Spirit of Dark Sanctuary changes its host on every turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't choose your attack Monster carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your {\i1}own army{\i0} will slowly tear your body to ribbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn... over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Ouija Board's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Message card...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D" and "E"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gathered two now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally {\i1}get{\i0} it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time your turn comes to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Ouija Board automatically adds another letter to your message of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you gather the "Death" letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still require three more of the Death Message cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only have one open slot on your Disk open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't go thinking you found a {\i1}weakness{\i0} in my strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Sanctuary doesn't just have the Onryou as its Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can now play both Magic and Trap Cards in the Monster Zone slots on the Disk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you can play up to ten Magic and Trap Cards at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Occult Combo is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Your life ends in three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape this fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! He's been completely cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he's got to do something about that Ouija Board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi has no clue what Monster on his field is being controlled by the Onryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he carelessly attacks, he'll only damage {\i1}himself{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he doesn't do anything about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} will lose in three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, is Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's {\i1}Yugi{\i0} we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sure to find a way out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I do {\b0}nothing{\b1}, you're bound to lose in three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Critter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I sacrifice Critter to the Dark Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to Critter's Special Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw one card from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then... who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pick the Magician girl again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you can't see it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one of my Monsters did he possess this turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be Kuriboh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knows it's not an offensive-type Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it Magnet Warrior...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it the Black Magician Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because of the Permanent Magic Card on his field, The Dark Door...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only attack with one Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since all I've drawn is a bunch of useless cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got no way to stop the Onryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But with Big Shield Gardna as my Wall Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there would be no point in possessing it, as it has only 100 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Shield Gardna in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you realized it yet, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to defend yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate to admit it, but he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've only got a few turns left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to pick one of these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hesitate now, I have no chance of beating Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Magnet Warrior Gamma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's just like him to make a wise move like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that won't work against {\b0}me{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Spirit of the Silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It possesses a Monster in Attack Mode, silences it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forces another Monster to take it's place, despite what the player orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Spirit! Possess the Magnet Warrior Gamma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Warrior Gamma can't attack or move,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so instead, my command to "attack" will be carried out by Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Black Magician girl is possessed by the spirit of Dark Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Burn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no flaw in my Occult Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Occult Combo is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} is really going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying Yugi is gonna lose over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... show me the form of a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, Yugi's in real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Yugi's Battle Phase has been completely sealed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will he have to waste his remaining turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and simply wait for "death" to come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Yugi will turn this situation around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't enough to break his Duelist's fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Occult Combo has no weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must be something I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My problem is the Onryou that keeps possessing my Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless I can get rid of the Onryou, I can't stop his Occult Combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how do I fight an enemy I can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can surrender if you want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Onryou becomes an Equipment Card on its opponent's Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Equipment Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two Reverse Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still continue on with your futile strategies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when the certainty of death awaits you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens in a Duel, I will always survive that one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I believe that the next turn always brings new possibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no "new possibilities"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Oujia Board's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third letter...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what're you gonna do, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be laughing anymore after {\i1}I'm{\i0} done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Souls of the Forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice you in order to maintain Dark Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, still standing on the brink of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just two turns, I'll see the distorted look of {\i1}fear{\i0} on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have gotten full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think you'd be {\i1}safer{\i0} keeping that superego of yours in check?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura... In my next two turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will {\i1}crush{\i0} your Occult Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally figured out how to strike back, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Yugi'd find a way outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I want to witness how you manage to get out of this with my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna crush my Occult Combo in just {\i1}two turns{\i0}, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give the tough-guy act up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one who's getting full of himself, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each new card holds a new possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duelist has as many possibilities as they have cards in their hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collected Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every Equipment Card on the field is now equipped with Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collected Power gathers every single Equipment Card on the field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and equips it to one selected Monster on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So by doing that, the Equipment Magic Card attached to Black Magician Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spellbook of Black Magic, is transfered to Kuriboh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's not {\b0}all{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said this yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That when the Onryou possesses a Monster, it becomes an Equipment Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I myself cannot see the form of this hateful spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Effect of Collected Power {\i1}forces{\i0} the Onryou to possess Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he could {\i1}do{\i0} that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exorcism!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It targets all Demon-type Monsters on the field and destroys them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Onryou attached to my Kuriboh is a Demon-type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the Hateful Spirit of Dark Sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Kuriboh it possesses are destroyed simultaneously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't get too cocky if I were you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you've completely broken my Occult Combo or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn isn't done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's still got one reverse card on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Go get 'im, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems he's found a major weak point in your Occult Combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know what Yugi's reverse card is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll {\i1}kill{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go{\i0} for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true your Occult Combo is close to flawless,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and you've done quite well covering up Dark Sanctuary's major draw back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the problem at hand is the activation conditions of Dark Sanctuary itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to activate Dark Sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark Necrofear must be in the Graveyard at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, if Dark Sanctuary were to suddenly {\b0}return{\b1} to the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark Sanctuary's Effect would disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure I need not say more for you to realize what his reverse card is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy your Occult Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Necrofear revives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Dark Necrofear has been brought back from the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Effect of Dark Sanctuary disappears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you are no longer permitted extra spaces on your Duel Disk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you return to the normal rules of only being allowed five Magic or Trap Cards on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've only got one space left...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I can directly attack you with this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Necrofear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Prey for Death" Gaze!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouija Board's Effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-E-A-T..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gathered four letters of the word "death".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll {\i1}never{\i0} get to play the last letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got no spot left to play the final piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to complete the message of "death",
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got no other choice than to remove The Dark Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment you even {\i1}try{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack you with all of my Monsters at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Occult Combo will be destroyed in one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any Monsters on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Yugi attacks me with all three of his Monsters right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not... possible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this match is decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're qualified to be Yugi's opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like you're at your rope's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I may have a trick or two left up my sleeves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your advice anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear already!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way {\i1}I{\i0} am gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to draw a card that'll turn this situation around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I have this card, you can't stop my Occult Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Bakura really still have a strategy left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't know when to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he just bluffing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what card did he draw...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,135)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi has succeeded in sealing Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Occult Combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} uses another strategy to bring Dark Sanctuary back to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means the final letter to the "Death" message can be completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Yugi'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, he's got no choice but to draw out that card this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smash the Darkness - God Attacks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
